{"tid":2356164,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（絲打入）有咩人生建議畀30歲以下嘅絲打？（2）","createTime":"2021-01-06T15:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T09:03:13.000Z","uid":131622,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a59d6b78486eccf969a03a9cadf414187e6fc2","tid":2356164,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:25:27.000Z","msg":"（絲打入）有咩人生建議畀30歲以下嘅絲打？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aHouLqU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aHouLqU</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">十大連登巴絲打畀30歲以下絲打嘅真實建議：</span></strong>（以下數據截至於2020/01/06）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>第1位 #7 山西布政司：</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">唔好旨意條仔/老公養，要獨立</span></strong>（1075 likes）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>第2位 # 18 淫底幼師：</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">情緒唔使放到好大 要你chur到盡先留得住嘅人 都唔會係長久... 反而真正愛你嘅會俾你hurt到...</span></strong>（756 likes）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>第3位 #13 HowieD：</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">留住隻豬呢啲要同10以下既絲打講</span></strong>（631 likes）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>第4位 #12 狂瘋掃落葉：</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">要愛人先要學識愛自己</span></strong>（489 likes）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>第5位 #6 成熟使用電腦：</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">定時check乳癌</span></strong>（474 likes）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>第6位 #9 你是電你是光：</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">搵到個有錢大隻靚仔專一先好嫁，寧缺莫濫。</span></strong>（294 likes）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>第7位 #45 醉曖.大黃貓：</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">唔好太主動，太主動嘅話證明對方都唔係好鍾意你＋當你知道對方唔鍾意你嘅時候，要止蝕</span></strong>（253 likes）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>第8位 #107 半隻迷途小羔羊：</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">要接受身體正常衰老＋無論有冇拍緊拖定曖昧緊，記得提高警覺，勿墮情網騙局，以免傷心傷身又傷金</span></strong>（241 likes）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>第9位 #22 黑命好撚貴：</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">買少啲唇膏</span></strong>（240 likes）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>第10位 #58 鄭欣宜：</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">青春有限＋就行你想行ge路 記住將來條路係自己揀的 所以唔好畀人左右你決定＋扮多d靚 因為到你去到30歲想扮都唔會及20歲時咁靚＋每個男人都係衰 揀到個愛自己又照顧到自己就mark實</span></strong>（226 likes）"},{"pid":"4a3383e34e1f6f0fae102dc0005288972f9632ac","tid":2356164,"uid":1024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033cb5f3ea65afd032b56b6914d3156b9e5e37eb","tid":2356164,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836eba526790650072c971f40d8632dd84d67881","tid":2356164,"uid":139763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T16:00:16.000Z","msg":"上個po有冇講要學投資？<br />\n(無追上個po)"},{"pid":"7798efd53567f8892076ac1634bdb89453eafddd","tid":2356164,"uid":131622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"836eba526790650072c971f40d8632dd84d67881","tid":2356164,"uid":139763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T16:00:16.000Z","msg":"上個po有冇講要學投資？<br />\n(無追上個po)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T16:02:55.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n<strong><ins>#68 耿爽不爽我很爽：</ins></strong><br />\n<blockquote>襯後生<br />\n快啲學投資 最好係美股<br />\n長期投資 買指數基金或者主題etf<br />\n每年10-20% 滾返幾年<br />\n複利效應下都幾和味<br />\n到時要上車都易啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"86ff1e819c9933d712dae88a286db03a2de4e593","tid":2356164,"uid":11681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T16:04:23.000Z","msg":"各位絲打認唔認為三十歲以下都要比屋企人管住哂？<br />\n例如出去過夜呢啲情況"},{"pid":"0909778acd8e8c8206aa6edf04768b6d6634d09c","tid":2356164,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86ff1e819c9933d712dae88a286db03a2de4e593","tid":2356164,"uid":11681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T16:04:23.000Z","msg":"各位絲打認唔認為三十歲以下都要比屋企人管住哂？<br />\n例如出去過夜呢啲情況"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T1